text: János Héder (20 October 1933 - 6 September 2014) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
